rows.label: qev085106_MSG0001
rows.name: Huh? That's not them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0002
rows.name: Doesn't look like it, no.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0003
rows.name: I'm sorry if we frightened you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0003_2
rows.name: My name is Elma. What's yours?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0005
rows.name: So the Ganglion were chasing these two?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0006
rows.name: Seems like it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0007
rows.name:
Are we correct in assuming that you're
hiding from the Ganglion?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0008
rows.name: If so, maybe we can help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0009
rows.name:
We come from a planet called Earth,
but now we're fighting the Ganglion here on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0010
rows.name: Really?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0011
rows.name: Pay them no heed, Rock![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0012
rows.name: I dunno, Celica. They don't really seem like the others...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0013
rows.name: It matters not. I shall not be fooled again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0014
rows.name: I'm picking up motion from deeper in.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0015
rows.name: Could be the Qlu girl and that Gaur.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0016
rows.name: Captain, look![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0017
rows.name: What are those humans doing there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0018
rows.name: Fall back! We'll return with reinforcements![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0019
rows.name: Ganglion ran away![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0020
rows.name: Let's stop them before more show up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085106_MSG0021
rows.name: Right![ST:wait ]
